- "Audit Trail" page displaying decision trace log
- `model_card_v1.md` — finalised, formatted
- `bias_report_v1.md` — finalised with real metrics
- `dpdp_compliance_onepager.pdf`
- `demo_script.md` — exact 10-minute click-path with talking points
- Screenshots of all 6 key screens

### Validation Criteria
- Every claim in the submission write-up has a corresponding screen or document in the submission package
- Model card shows real metrics (not placeholder text)
- DPDP one-pager maps every requirement to a named control
- Demo script runs in ≤ 10 minutes without hesitation on first dry-run

### Risk of Delay
- Governance documentation quality is lower priority and gets deprioritised
